content:
This table shows all possible experience sources for Thieving in the game, as well as all interactions that require a Thieving level. It also lists the items involved in the interactions, as well as other skills involved in processing the item.

While some of these entries may be listed as Free-to-play, the only thieving-related action that may be done on Free-to-play worlds is unlocking the Port Sarim Jail door, which grants no Thieving experience on those worlds. NPCs cannot be pickpocketed when not on a Members server.
